WEBVTT

00:00:03.857 --> 00:00:06.095
Chris Anderson: Welcome
to the TED Interview.

00:00:06.119 --> 00:00:07.386
I'm Chris Anderson.

00:00:07.976 --> 00:00:11.523
This is the podcast series
where I sit down with a TED speaker,

00:00:11.547 --> 00:00:13.791
and we get to dive much deeper
into their ideas

00:00:13.815 --> 00:00:16.078
than was possible during their TED Talk.

00:00:16.090 --> 00:00:17.460
(Music)

00:00:17.502 --> 00:00:21.279
Today's guest is something
of a personal hero:

00:00:21.303 --> 00:00:22.454
David Deutsch.

00:00:22.478 --> 00:00:24.494
He's a physicist, an author.

00:00:24.518 --> 00:00:28.485
He has a reputation of being
something of a reclusive genius.

00:00:28.887 --> 00:00:32.704
He lives by himself in a home in Oxford
working late into the night,